{"tid":1467482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全部入晒黎]大家應該休息兩日，星期五六日再黎","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:01.000Z","uid":6375,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5445174fd774af561a7a03bc1b76e25af399056b","tid":1467482,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:11.000Z","msg":"先作利申 核彈都唔撚割<br />\n<br />\n但我認為真係要停兩日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 我地要換過一批受影響旅客</span></span><br />\n以提高影響成個機場經濟體系嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">持續性</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 重整軍心</span></span><br />\n大家今晚嘅氣氛 情緒 太過高漲<br />\n但高漲唔係壞事<br />\n有利有弊<br />\n救女仔 fit popo就係好好例子<br />\n但好易做錯決定 亦好易影響身邊嘅戰友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 挽回「真&middot;和理非」對機場嘅信心</span></span><br />\n大家都應該見到坐喺arrival hall，有好多婆婆，或者帶埋小朋友嘅父母<br />\n佢地會出席，就係覺得機場安全，POPO唔敢亂黎<br />\n但經過今日，點都會令到一部份手足跌眼鏡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家要記住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場係一個淨係多人佔領 就搞得掂嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n癱瘓機場 就會癱瘓經濟<br />\n癱瘓完第日個市跌就緊架喇<br />\n唔洗暴力就贏嘅地方<br />\n大家要識利用<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不被捕"},{"pid":"7d53b3e9f39126413cb34b042c57a236c77fb6b9","tid":1467482,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"12ff38b0dab639c1860848dd0e1f167a0ffbc7a6","tid":1467482,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fe58c8f9e6f2dc0b30e41ce97639957368b834d6","tid":1467482,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e293e96247fb2e0352742b9799c0e9ff058ed6ab","tid":1467482,"uid":6375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:32.000Z"